COREY MANDEL

Mortgage Agent

Level 2

  • 647.200.7588
  • corey.mandel@vinegroup.ca
  • English
  • Toronto

With eagerness and experience in the mortgage industry, Corey Mandel is a seasoned professional who is excited to be helping countless clients in Ontario achieve their homeownership dreams. Corey started his journey in the mortgage industry as a Marketing Director for some of Ontario’s top boutique mortgage brokerages, gaining invaluable insights into the ins and outs of Ontario mortgages and the Canadian real estate market.

Driven by his passion for helping people and armed with extensive guidance, knowledge and skills, Corey became a licensed agent to take his commitment to his clients to the next level. Since then, Corey has continued his journey of building a name and brand, granting the ability to find financing solutions for borrowers across Ontario, helping borrowers achieve beyond their expectations. Now, with the prestigious Vine Group Mortgage Brokerage, Corey takes pride in providing unparalleled and unmatched mortgage services, focusing on tailored mortgage solutions. Whether you are a first-time homebuyer, a self-employed individual, or someone with credit challenges, Corey has the expertise and experience to find the right mortgage solution for you.

Corey’s mission is to guide his clients through the mortgage process with professionalism, transparency, and exceptional customer service. He is committed to building long-term relationships with our clients based on trust, integrity, and results. With Corey, you can expect a seamless and stress-free mortgage experience. He provides comprehensive mortgage services, including mortgage pre-approvals, mortgage refinancing, mortgage renewals, and more. When you choose to work with Corey, you can be confident that you are working with a dedicated and experienced mortgage professional who will work tirelessly to help you achieve your homeownership goals.

#QualifyWithCor
